column5: Is there a list of lakes available over the internet of lakes in North West Ontario which gives names, size and location?I realize that there are many lakes with the same name, but when I hear or read something in a post, it would be nice to be able to find it on a map.Thanks,Fritz
Hello FritzThanks for the road construction update.If you go to www.ontariosunsetcountry.ca you can request a free map which gives all the lakes and camps. It is very detailed.Jeff
I could not get this site [www.ontariosunsetcountry.ca]Came up as no longer available ,any faults?
